          "title": "Immediate issues",
          "reviewText": "Bought these for my son for his birthday.  He wore them once.  The opening around the waist tie shredded, which Lulu's support team said was wear and tear and wouldn't replace. I tried to stitch back up to save them - it is most definitely not wear and tear but absolutely the quality of the fabric. When I said it was shredded, I mean shredded.  There is no way one wear took a toll like that.  We do love Lululemon products on the whole, but these were a huge disappointment.",
