        {
          "title": "Changed the design in 2023 sometime",
          "reviewText": "I have several pairs of these I bought 5 years ago.  I love them.  The best shorts money could buy.\n\nI got another pair in 2023 as a gift.  They never fit right so I hardly wore them thinking it was a size problem.  I tried to buy two more pairs a month ago.  Same fit problem as those that I got as a gift. A little googling later and it turns out that Lulemon changed the design.  \n\nThat fit change: \n- the waist sits higher on my hips \n- the liner is loose and provides zero support for anything.",
